problem:
\begin{problem*}{}{}
  The real numbers $x_1,x_2,\ldots,x_{2025}$ satisfy,
  \[
    x_1+x_2=2x_{\sigma(1)}, x_2+x_3=2{x_{\sigma(2)}},
    \ldots, x_{2025}+x_1=2{x_{\sigma(2025)}}
  .\]
  Where $(\sigma(1), \sigma(2),\ldots,\sigma(2025))$ is a
  permutation of $(1,2,\ldots,2025)$.
  Prove that $x_1=x_2=\cdots=x_{2025}$.
\end{problem*}
